author: IANS
title: 'Game of Thrones' star Emilia Clarke goes topless
text:
London:  'Game of Thrones' star Emilia Clarke has heated up the cover of Esquire magazine's 'Sexiest Woman Alive' issue by posing topless.


Emilia Clarke. Pic/Santa Banta 

Lying topless in a luxurious bed, with a small blanket covering her bottom, the actress is seen with her open hair on the cover. Inside the issue, the 28-year-old is seen in a lingerie, reports eonline.com.
"Half pal, half dominatrix. Half kid sister, half sexy queen. The movie star who plays, in her real life, an anonymous, funny beauty," writer Benjamin Markovits shares in the November issue. "This is the gorgeous balance of Emilia Clarke."
